  "description": "¶Original Post ¶Part 1 There\u0026rsquo;s some new post from some academic about how academic intellectuals should look toward Gramsci\u0026rsquo;s \u0026ldquo;organic intellectual\u0026rdquo; in order to do their duty against rising fascism.\nI\u0026rsquo;m not linking it because I think it\u0026rsquo;s hot trash, so instead I\u0026rsquo;ll link my own writing, that explains how the narrative around Stop City City doesn\u0026rsquo;t line up at all with the experiences of those who tried to stop Cop City, and how Gramsci\u0026rsquo;s idea of the organic intellectual may have been co-opted by American intelligence before his writing was even translated into English!\n",
